  m_text: "It's the year 3001 in a galaxy \nnot too far away....\n\nThe flagship
    Gastromandy has fallen. With the crew captured, the navigation system and the
    turrets are locked on emergency warp, but the cannon systems are totally manual.
    Only you, the ship\u2019s panicked head chef remains to defend the galley. \nYou
    have no idea how to fire a laser, but you know how to cook. \n\nWeaponize the
    galaxy\u2019s deadliest spices! It's time to load the cannons and blast the invaders
    on your way!\n\nSurvive the escape, as long as you can!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0d53d8bfa0549df44a3aab851e0f0b6b, type: 2}
